Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.79,0:00:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在我還小的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.54,0:00:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}腦海中就常浮現出「影像」來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是在何處都感覺似曾相識的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有好幾次都是有著水的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.84,0:00:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是夢中的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可我並不曾去過那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.92,0:00:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}據說是因為受到了因克拉布的反菲米娜斯的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其實真正原因是什麼 我並不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是我曾想尋找些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以 我踏上了旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}緊急情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}受到碎石帶的撞擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5因為是邊境就沒有清理者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.97,0:00:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜託了 理音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.16,0:00:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}控制船體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.06,0:00:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}保持船體平衡後立刻進行短距離跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜託了 帶我到那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還差… 一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.32,0:01:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在預計降落地點有生命反應？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.23,0:01:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我一定在追尋那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}七海姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}七海姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…柑菜醬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 姐姐我做了個怪夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}居然夢到小海他在光芒之中和一個裸女抱在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了 看起來很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不不 應該說是很美的一個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了 剛好就像那邊那個女孩子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}七海姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能說明一下那究竟是怎麼回事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我先說在前頭 希望你們別誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哪門子誤會？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你現在心裡想的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總之 她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貴月一夏學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是那位今天轉學到我們學校三年級的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正確
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是叫貴月一夏嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}初次見面 我是小海的姐姐七海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}確實是「打擾」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後 明明今天在剛認識的學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼會在海的家裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這…這是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}事實上由於庫安連環的故障
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}造成奧爾他雷特出現嚴重的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}並且因克拉布也有嚴重的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太複雜了姐姐我不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}簡單來說 就是因為一些事情 沒有住的地方了 並且也沒帶錢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我回家的時候偶然碰上學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}聽說了她的困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就想姑且讓她暫住一晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為不能放著她不管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼能讓女孩子一個人在野外露宿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}提問 為什麼在玄關那裡抱在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我才不知道這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒？你知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同學他的奧爾他雷特…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 是因為他好像不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我就在照顧他…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.95,0:04:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我那時候好像確實不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:04:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昏過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小海 你生病了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不知道 現在沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}照顧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是照顧嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在身邊照料又抱在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是如同字面上的照顧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an8}（日語照顧寫作介抱）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是抱一抱病就能好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在我的星球就是這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的星球？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…是說我的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貴月同學是來自哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}布雷爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 是來自北邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是北海道那邊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…還要更遠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是在留學嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 從那麼遠的地方一個人來留學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貴月同學真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}日語也說得這麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然不太明白 大概還是理解了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:05:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:06:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過如果有事聯繫老家的父母不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…這…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…有什麼難言之隱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐我大概明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.11,0:06:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}超能力！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貴月同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 一夏醬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉啊 讓你想起傷心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我和海人也失去了雙親…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以一夏醬的感受我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏醬的感受…我是非常明白啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等…七海姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好啦 總之就是剛才說的那些原因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姑且讓學姐住一晚上 可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別說一晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}住這不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}七海姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你想 我明天開始就要出遠差了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}本來就想著要有誰來照顧小海來著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.06,0:06:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}同一個學校的人也比較放心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:06:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又是女孩子還能做做飯 洗洗衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真可靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}七海姐不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}同齡男女居然同住一個屋檐下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}困難時就該互相幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且小海是個溫柔的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不管是和多漂亮的學姐住一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也不會做那種奇怪的事 這種奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有那種奇怪的事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不會做的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}當…當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 剛才結巴了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你還想了想是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才沒想啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你這眼神明擺著在說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我這眼神是什麼眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你這種就是那種！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就定了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小女未經世事 還請多多關照 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}叫我姐就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像…媳婦進門一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我送谷川回家去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你好像…生氣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個啊…谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.49,0:08:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}關於學姐這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}助人為樂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是幫助了遇上麻煩的學姐而已是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 是啊…僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}送到這就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天…見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 那個美女學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}居然寄住在霧島同學家裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是怎麼回事啊 柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像不知不覺就變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過霧島同學家裡還有家人一起的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}他姐姐明天開始要出遠差
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂喂 真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}劇情急轉直下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}該怎麼辦啊 哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這下就定了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}定了…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:09:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天碰頭的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}飯做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…那個姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她說要打包行李 就先回房了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}義大利麵和味噌湯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}標準搭配吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}搭配之外的標準搭配吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我搞錯什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒…沒事吧？不好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…與其說是不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這味道酸酸的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是…冷麵？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想著你今天累壞了還是吃點涼的比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:10:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊不 因為嚐到了意想不到的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}稍微有點吃驚而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我繼續吃了哦 這份冷義大利麵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我能問你個問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐你為什麼來這裡留學的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為有想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哪裡呢 是這附近嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不如讓我帶你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.28,0:10:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個啊…我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不知道是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.76,0:10:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有樹有池塘…是個沒什麼特別之處的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那該怎樣找呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也對呢 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我就是想去那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真繁忙的一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天碰頭會會遇到大家呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}該怎麼說明呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說 這究竟是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}增加了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這麼說來 剛剛也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是抱一抱病就能好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}擁…抱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哎呀哎呀 這可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}得趕快進行治療…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}痛痛 痛痛 都飛走喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}親…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}騙你的 這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看來修不好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音 庫安連環的狀況如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}完全出BUG了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我從沒有後悔過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}既然都到了這星球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不知是不是因為太累
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我一躺下 很快就入睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}連夢也沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同學 海人同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快起來 海人同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐她就要出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已經這麼晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎…怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你這件衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從姐姐那裡借過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.26,0:12:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這邊的睡衣…真有點讓人害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對對對對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小海 姐姐我就走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你再不來送行我就哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}馬…馬上就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人 小心身體 別亂花錢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還要好好學習 跟朋友們好好相處 別熬夜 可能會寂寞 但還是要保重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏醬 小海就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我說 火車進站了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}終於走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人 你寂寞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也許…有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回去之前想繞去個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想去的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐拜託的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被姐姐她？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有自己的衣服到總是不方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然有些地方有點怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}確實是個可愛的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要有了這些就夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你 我今天很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然購物就是女生最愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.18,0:14:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也得和姐姐道聲謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等她打電話過來的時候說就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 就這麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦 門開著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀 真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等得都不耐煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喲 歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是說好了要開電影製作的誓師大會嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉了 我們擅自就選了你家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不是說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 這麼快就親親密密去購物了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.76,0:14:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再說你們究竟是怎麼進來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我建議你還是換一把更牢固的鎖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別隨便就開人家門
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你這完全就是犯罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哎呀 因為必須要好好調查嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我摯友寄宿的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你為什麼會知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}趁所有人都在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.05,0:15:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}由雄心勃勃的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就霧島海人的處女作的內容進行討論吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}既然開始了就快說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來 導演
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說 為什麼由她來主持啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什麼啦 又是高年級的學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 究竟要拍怎樣的電影呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.73,0:15:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就把我寫的這本劇本拍成電影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}順便說一下 這是我構思二十年 寫了五年…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是什麼樣的故事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是講二十三世紀 機動兵器活躍於世界各地的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就連好萊塢也要嚇得屁滾尿流的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:16:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一代商業大作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拍不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}全都用CG來做你放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}或許不需要攝影機也有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還是拍些簡單點更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就校園之類的怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學校的批准姑且還是能批下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}確實是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}劇情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣的又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學校裡突然出現喪屍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}僥倖生還的主人公們…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拍不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏學姐不提提意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你這傢伙膽子不小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是主演嘛 說說你的意見嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然不是說故事方面的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但我想看些美麗的風景吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我才來這裡沒多久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想去很多很多的地方 見識各種各樣的新鮮事物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為有我有想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不好意思 說得太抽象了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到處逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:16:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}反正就快到暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:16:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.92,0:17:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}玩樂與拍電影 一石二鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我覺得最後肯定都變成玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就那樣也不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也不是一定就要拍一部電影出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到處去轉轉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}或許能找到你想要去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你 海人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}電影的內容遲點再想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家先一起為預祝電影拍攝成功而乾杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這飲料是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是奇怪的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.42,0:17:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過有點甜甜的 還是挺好喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我還要一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我帶了很多來 喜歡喝就盡情喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:17:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}炸彈！牌也出完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吶 檸檬學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個飲料叫什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}「活力」飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原來如此啊 真讓人上癮嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈哈哈…活力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐 沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總感覺有點兒暈暈的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}暈暈的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 身體有點兒熱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}身體發熱嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那可真不妙呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂！兩個獨處的人在幹什麼呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到這邊來！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎…怎麼了啊 谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剛才你肯定覺得我妨礙你們了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是不是！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.51,0:19:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那學姐覺得呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒這麼想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要在這寄住的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只有兩個人在一起住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}馬上就快到暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}兩個人一整天都獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}獨處！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我就開門見山的問了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐你覺得海人怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒？這…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海…海人同學在我困難的時候幫了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不是指這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是問你覺得他怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.34,0:20:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎…怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個是什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}生體…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是我的寵物…叫理音…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.50,0:20:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}竟然會有這樣動物  我肯定暈了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣也挺可愛的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且還在跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.34,0:20:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正好在興頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來玩我特製的國王遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.84,0:20:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喔！聽起來不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}國王遊戲是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}玩一下就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誰是國王！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那先來一個程度輕點兒的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}3號 彈1號的腦門 下手重一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}4號 打1號耳光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人你這笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.99,0:20:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼總是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.97,0:20:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}5號 和4號親親
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}3號 脫褲子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}收到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 不要給我們看你的內褲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}變態！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}4號 做個誘惑的姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}2號
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.93,0:21:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和1號…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}H
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家這樣很不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}感覺能拍成很棒的電影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.57,0:21:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…嗯…沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…我已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.71,0:21:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.98,0:21:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.86,0:21:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那飲料是怎麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.84,0:21:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}突然…頭…好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.47,0:21:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:21:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐 真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}稍微…把眼睛閉一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:18.96,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.83,0:22:21.61,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦？不疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:24.21,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.05,0:22:32.91,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}笨蛋…小海…這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.96,0:22:36.57,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我才是個笨蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.88,0:22:39.88,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.11,0:22:43.56,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.01,0:22:44.87,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.97,0:22:47.60,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.91,0:22:51.18,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可以說出來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.88,0:22:53.84,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.23,0:22:56.23,副本Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.44,0:23:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜 霧島同學今天請假了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.54,0:23:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不行！一定要去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是最優先事項！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…你說了這句不能說的台詞…

