Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.49,0:22:43.99,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)\3c&H4B34D7&}緊繫於你 愈纏愈緊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.99,0:22:51.51,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)\3c&HCD6A1D&\t(2864,3156,\3c&H0090FF)}若我不曾躊躇 對你說出那句話來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.51,0:22:57.64,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)\3c&HDB6CEB&\t(2551,3000,\3c&H77BD3E)}你已經不哭了嗎？
